Note: Usage Example
Note:
Example: Enabling and monitoring a plugin
Let manager be create_plugin_manager()
If manager.enable_plugin("example_plugin"):
    Log message "Plugin enabled successfully: example_plugin"
    Let stats be manager.monitor_plugin("example_plugin")
    Log message "Plugin stats: " plus stats
Otherwise:
    Log error message "Failed to enable plugin: example_plugin"
:End Note 